---
title: HelloHero: Pork Schnitzel & Tomato Salad with Creamy Roast Potatoes & Beetroot Relish
description: We’re putting a pep in this pork schnitzel’s step by adding some Nan's seasoning to the golden panko crumb. Serve up with
creamy roast baby potatoes to really make this dish dance and you’ll be bounding to the dinner table in excitement.
